## 📁 DOCUMENTATION STRUCTURE DISCIPLINE

**JANGAN bikin dokumen sembarangan.** Sebelum create/update dokumen:

### Current Folder Structure:
```
docs/                    ← Project docs (by domain)
  ├── guides/            ← Quick fixes, server access
  ├── reports/           ← Audit & verification reports
  ├── planning/          ← Feature plans & roadmap
  ├── *.md              ← Root docs: API_RESPONSE_STANDARD, REBRANDING_PLAN, E2E_TESTING_REPORT

.opencode/               ← Agent instructions (opencode)
  ├── rules/             ← Modular .mdc rule files

.github/workflows/       ← CI/CD workflows (deploy, ssh-command)
```

### Naming Rules:
- `.opencode/rules/` → `NN-descriptive-name.mdc` (00-task-framework.mdc)
- `docs/` → `UPPERCASE.md` for standalone, `snake_case.md` for inside folders
- Root `.md` → `DESCRIPTIVE-NAME.md`

### DO NOT:
- ❌ Create new subfolders tanpa alasan jelas
- ❌ Duplicate docs (update existing, or link)
- ❌ Orphan files (harus referenced di `docs/README.md` index)
- ❌ Inconsistent casing

