## 🎯 CHECKLIST BEFORE CLAIM "DONE"

**Development Work:**
- [ ] Fase 1: Task understood, no ambiguity
- [ ] Fase 2: Source verified dari code, bukan asumsi
- [ ] Fase 3: Scope tertulis jelas, senggolan dimapped
- [ ] Fase 4: Only in-scope files touched
- [ ] Fase 5: Test PASS + manual smoke done
- [ ] Fase 6: Report include test results + files changed

**Documentation (if any created/updated):**
- [ ] Folder sudah existing, tidak bikin baru
- [ ] File naming consistent (kebab-case / UPPERCASE)
- [ ] Tidak ada duplikasi doc di tempat lain
- [ ] File ter-reference di index/README
- [ ] Folder structure clean (no orphan files)

**Code Quality:**
- [ ] No `dd()`, `var_dump()`, debug statements
- [ ] Type hints complete
- [ ] Permission checks present
- [ ] Validation in place
- [ ] Error handling proper
- [ ] No hardcoded secrets
- [ ] Follows AGENTS.md code style

